---

- Use librosa for audio analysis when needed
- Handle different audio formats appropriately (mp3, wav, flac, etc.)
- Consider memory usage for large audio files
- Use appropriate sample rates and bit depths
- Use pandas for structured data analysis
- Use numpy for numerical computations
- Consider performance for large datasets
- Use matplotlib or seaborn for plotting with consistent color schemes
- Include proper labels and legends in visualizations
- Use context managers for file operations
- Validate audio file formats and handle errors gracefully